node.title: Legendary jockey Glen Boss announces retirement
node.alt: Jockey on a race horse winning a Melbourne Cup.
node.description: Glen Boss calls time on a decorated careerÂ which included three consecutive Melbourne Cup wins on board Makybe Diva.
node.content: ["Glen Boss \u2014 who rode Makybe Diva to three consecutive Melbourne Cup wins \u2014 has announced he will retire\u00a0after a Caulfield race meeting this weekend.", "Boss guided Makybe Diva to her three Melbourne Cup victories between 2003 and 2005.", "He also won a host of other prominent races, including the Cox Plate, the VRC Derby and the Golden Slipper.", "His final race meeting will be the Zipping Classic at Caulfield on Saturday.", "More to come."]
